data.description:
Welcome to the highly sought-after Oakleaf plantation! this property offers resort-style amenities that will make you feel like you're on vacation every day. Dive into multiple pools, keep fit on the tennis courts, let the kids have a blast at the playgrounds, or cool off in the splash pad - the options are endless!

Step inside this impeccable 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem and be greeted by gorgeous wood look tile flooring throughout the first level. The spacious kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring stunning granite counters and a custom backsplash that will make cooking and entertaining a breeze. Upstairs, you'll discover all three bedrooms, including a luxurious primary suite that will be your personal retreat. With its spacious layout, on-suite bathroom boasting a soaking tub and walk-in shower, and ample natural light, this bedroom is a sanctuary of relaxation.

After a long day, unwind on your screened lanai, where you can sip on your favorite beverage and enjoy the pleasant Florida weather. Plus, with a brand new HVAC system and a roof that's only 5 months old, you can have peace of mind knowing that this home is move-in ready and maintenance-free. 

Schedule your tour today to experience the resort lifestyle you've always dreamed of!
